    What is in the box?

  • Laptop backpack only

    • Product Description

    DESCRIPTION

    Light weight and spacious laptop backpack with 2 compartments and 1 front easy-access pocket. One compartment is for carrying laptop inside with padding for safety and space for laptop accessories like charger, etc. Other compartment has organiser for pens, visiting cards, etc along with space for carrying papers, files, etc. It has provision for holding bottles on both sides and has padded shoulder straps for your comfort.
